Day 12. Post positive #Covid test day... 05/05/20 (Tuesday)
Early am coughing fit; needed my back pummelled. Didn’t get up too late. Meds, inhalers. breakfast and tea. Felt quite shaky in my core today; quite breathless on exertion, stairs, quick movements; went to bed for a bit.
